{"tid":2233814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際戰線］新鮮共產黨澳洲出爐！","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:33:47.000Z","uid":274317,"like":220,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"5d06204d86d4522358314b4e6dd67b8fc8d9791e","tid":2233814,"uid":274317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"是共產黨，新鮮的共產黨。<br />\n(成日叫人唔好干涉內政的共產黨)<br />\n<br />\n澳洲區選都聽到中文？！<br />\n<br />\n點解澳洲地區選舉會有個中国人選、仲要畀人發現佢同共產黨商會有聯繫都可以選嘅？！<br />\n<br />\n個故事似曾相識？咪Liberal MP 廖嬋娥囉。<br />\n呢啲，先係真正嘅干涉內政。<br />\n<br />\nRead more about Li Zhang: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VHKTSA/photos/a.105632170787348/357603542256875/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FVHKTSA%2Fphotos%2Fa.105632170787348%2F357603542256875%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=68ebce90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/VHKTSA/photos/a.105632170787348/357603542256875/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nNow this is CCP infiltration (not even hiding)<br />\n<br />\nAllowing people like Li Zhang for Tucker Ward to be elected doesn&rsquo;t mean one person with a CCP background is in charge of the community, it means the ENTRIE SYSTEM OF THE CCP furthering on hold of Australian&rsquo;s resources and general welfare.<br />\n<br />\nGladys Liu MP (from HK) was a perfect example.<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://fb.com/vhktsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fvhktsa&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=5a4eb5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/vhktsa</a><br />\nInstagram: @vhktsa<br />\nTelegram: @vhktsa<br />\nEmail: 2020vhktsa@gmail.com"},{"pid":"3a0307112a0d680e1d167bbfd56aa5f5922402b8","tid":2233814,"uid":274317,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"原link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.